## FuelPay Admin Panel (Vite) environment variables
## Copy this file to `.env.local` (recommended).

# Preferred: set full base URL (must include protocol)
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.fuelpay.charge-one.uz/

# Alternative (if you want host/port split)
# VITE_API_PROTOCOL=https
# VITE_API_HOST=api.fuelpay.charge-one.uz
# VITE_API_PORT=

